Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:23.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}わたしに できること
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ひとつづつ叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:32.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}夢に向かって 一歩ずつ歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.76,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}わたしにできること
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あなたにも伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:44.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あきらめないで　翼広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:51.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}さあ　とぼうよ　あしたのために
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:01:00.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}もうヤダッて　ひざを抱えて嘆くときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:05.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}だいじょうぶ　泣かないで　きっとできる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:11.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}勇気のとびら　ちょっと開けるだけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:14.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}笑顔ギュッと抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:20.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}高く高く　舞い上がれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:23.77,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}わたしにも できること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}やさしさを 守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:32.81,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}涙ふいたら飛び立とう　明日へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}わたしから 届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:38.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}とっておきの魔法で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:44.32,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}もう　うつむかない　ヤクソクするわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:50.49,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}自由のため　未来のために
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:23.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我期待力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}件件都能成真
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:32.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向着梦想  一步步前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我希望力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}都能向你传达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:44.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}永不放弃  张开翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:51.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为了明天  快快飞翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:01:00.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}就算厌倦了  紧抱双膝叹息时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:05.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}也别担心  不要哭泣  一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:11.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}勇气之门  微微开启一条小缝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:14.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}紧紧拥抱笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:20.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}高高地  飞扬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:23.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我渴望尽力去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}守护这份温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:32.81,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}擦干眼泪一飞冲天  向明天前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我想用秘藏的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:38.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:44.32,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}约定好  不能再低头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:50.49,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为了自由  为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------ED---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:40.02,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}きみのなかに わたしをずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:42.62,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ブックマークしてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:45.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}笑いながら頑張った、と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.39,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}めちゃくちゃ ほめてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:51.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}どんな時も 全部本気
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.38,0:22:54.09,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ギャップにも 驚かないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:57.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}たった今を 進まなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:59.91,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}未来もないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:05.62,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}タタカイの意味 アタタカイなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:08.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}闘いぬくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:18.41,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}闘いなどない わたしたちの 世界のために！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:24.37,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}きみとなら きっと できること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:30.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ココロとココロで 手を結んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.69,0:23:35.64,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}運命線 ぎゅっと かさねたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:45.41,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}夢への共犯者　どこまででも 翔べそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.29,0:23:54.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}眠れる翼を 信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:40.02,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}要一直把我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:42.62,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}存储在你心中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:45.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}要笑着说努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}好好地夸奖一番哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:51.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}无论何时 都一本正经
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.38,0:22:54.09,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}有差距 也不惊奇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:57.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}正所谓少壮不努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:59.91,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}老大徒伤悲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:05.62,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}战争的意义 若是火热的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:08.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}抛弃它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:18.41,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我们的世界  不需要战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:24.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}要是和你一起 一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:30.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我们手牵手 就像心连心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.69,0:23:35.64,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}生命线 紧紧相叠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:45.41,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我们是通向梦想的共犯 无论到何处 都展翅高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.29,0:23:54.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}相信那  眠之翼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第6话\N「在一起哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸上堆满了不愉快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂本少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专程把我们叫来还以为出了什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果居然是要我们削减预算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想叫我怎么愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也很急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直只能把战果拱手让给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙眼中只有自己脚底下那点利益
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是异形军没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在那些人说不定正在互相残杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同世界大战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  宫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得本打算带你逛逛不列颠城市的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想  军队真是无奇不有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你们听到什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是萨尼娅的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接近基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是来接我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉萨尼娅好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个很好的孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌也唱得很好不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了萨尼娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西正注视着这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答时要吐字清晰  嗓音洪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狼星方向有架所属不明的飞行物接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是异形军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我觉得不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这速度不是一般的飞机所能达到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是看不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它藏在云层中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标不能用肉眼确认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要  要怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么可做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有飞行脚我们无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道它们的目标是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异形军的行动不会有那么狡诈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标仍然高速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离接触大约还有3分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅  援兵来之前你只负责拖时间就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量避免发生冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始引开目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别硬撑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅知道异形军在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她似乎连地平线以下的东西都能看得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才经常安排她进行夜间巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的治愈魔法如出一辙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚听到她的歌声了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是她的一种魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她用歌声来引导运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不进行反击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对看不到的敌人也做得这么出色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就看不到什么异形军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅说的话肯定错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅  够了  返航吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人做的很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下的好大  能见度真低
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等艾拉  别擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 让她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗似乎结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这次的异形军除萨尼娅以外谁都没看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直藏在云层里没有出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有任何反击…这可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是异形军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个害羞的异形军…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  正好同性相吸也说不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然连异形军究竟为何物都不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来无论出现什么都不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败后的异形军连续出现的概率极高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有必要暂时安排倒班以应对夜战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始我任命你们为夜间专属班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是经历过这次战斗的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只在一旁看看而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是是  我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  那加上艾拉一共3个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我把异形军放跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀是蓝莓  但为什么有这么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老家寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝莓对视力有益哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  听说在不列颠执行夜航的飞行员经常吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳佳  夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸舌头  舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不堪入目…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做事要有分寸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了些什么啊艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  早餐已经吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为晚上做准备  去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,330)}萨尼娅的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,330)}兼·临时夜班专员集合处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才睡醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于把房间都弄得这么暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让我们尽快习惯黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了  把萨尼娅的房间弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平时没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个就像符一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,符？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免怪物幽灵进入的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常被认作是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜航的时候这种事很常见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算不飞也会被这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是不知道我是否存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个狂妄四眼的话别往心里去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是无聊就玩塔罗牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔罗牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能使用预知未来的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也只是不久之后将发生的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是马上能与最想见的人相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想见的人已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚了  快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是为了让眼睛适应黑暗环境的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金盏花的香草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说这对眼睛也是有好处的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是民间传说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是从我祖母的祖母的祖母那里传下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道跟山椒一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山椒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳佳  丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再吐次舌头看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是想和谁比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哆嗦停不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到夜晚的天空如此黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次夜间飞行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可… 可以牵着手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是萨尼娅能牵着我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没做好心理准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放手啊  决不能放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿越到云层上方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人肯定飞不了这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  萨尼娅  艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  这是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼肝油  从八目鳗中提取的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富含很多维他命对眼睛很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好腥气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是鱼身上提炼的油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营养的话就别在乎味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是一如既往的宫藤式粗俗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  带这东西来的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能喝此等美味真是十分感激
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机油就是这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚来的时候被强迫喝这个  真是为难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很能理解您那时的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉和萨尼娅的故乡在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是修姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是欧罗沙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修姆斯在欧洲北部  欧罗沙在东部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说欧洲大部分地区都被异形军侵略了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我生活的城市在很久前就沦陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都背井离乡  到向更东部去避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻越乌拉尔山脉  直到山的对面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什么啊  你有没有在听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算现在彼此分离  但总有一天还能团聚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  欧罗沙可是很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌拉尔山东麓可有扶桑的几十倍大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找人不是说说这么容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说那边还有异形军的巢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样我也很羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为萨尼娅盼望着能快点和家人团聚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么萨尼娅的家人也一定盼望着与你相见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两方都不放弃的话  总有一天能相聚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:14:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这么想一想就很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们干脆去蒸桑拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑拿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫藤不知道桑拿是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和刚刚没什么分别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在修姆斯  人们喜欢桑拿胜过浴室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅皮肤好白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朝哪边看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常穿一身黑衣反而更显眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用那种眼神看萨尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑拿之后冲个凉可是绝配
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确凉凉的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别害羞啊  都是女生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会心动吗  宫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为打扰到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这歌真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从前爸爸为我作的一首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候  雨一直下个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了打发无聊 数雨滴声的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸以此作了一首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅通过父亲的推荐  在维也纳攻读音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫藤的父亲也很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的飞行脚是宫藤博士为了你而量身定做的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是这点就很羡慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 既然要送能送可爱点的东西就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奢侈啊  飞行脚可是很贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没告诉我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生日也是父亲的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉会很麻烦就没跟大家提
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候快乐的事优先啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫藤  好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好像听到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广播的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上天空会安静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到从山对面或是地平线那边传来的广播
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好厉害  这样也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  夜晚飞行的时候我一直都在听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们两人的秘密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  但今晚是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说  今天也是萨尼娅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是异形军的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学萨尼娅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该正进行着夜间飞行训练
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宫藤她们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上把她们叫回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状态根本不知道在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  敌人的目标是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人吗萨尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是异形军吗  在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩快去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你一个人想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的目标是我  不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开我  在一起的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨尼娅告诉我敌人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我能预测敌人的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不是萨尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然它是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但萨尼娅你不孤独哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝对不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异形军处于连接织女牵牛星的鹊桥上方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正快速直线接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离大约3200
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在加速  再瞄得近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  还有3秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要击中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打偏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  速度降低了  机体受损了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  快显形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉  不行  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这闲工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺聪明的嘛  宫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我们一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是团队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能听到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  不是已经解决了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  这是爸爸的钢琴声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是广播
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天空的某个角落传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了  真是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  或许不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是萨尼娅的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确说来  是昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是和我一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对喜欢萨尼娅的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮她庆祝生日再正常不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界某处有这些人在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事也很正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉真温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈  萨尼娅在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐萨尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐宫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的异形军明显是针对萨尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还模仿她的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对异形军必须重新认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得上层对此事知道多少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们掌握了许多我们不知道的内情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再稀里糊涂的了  吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\fs21}15岁了\N芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\fs21}萨尼娅\N14岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.11,0:24:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳佳小得像豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉大得如南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽奈恰到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形色具佳是巴克霍隆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.85,0:24:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7话\N「微风轻抚」

